sentences: Having no formal musical training, Kevon and Kory Hart were introduced to the process of composing music digitally in the year 2004 through a former school mate.
In the years to follow, the duo would hone their songwriting and production skills in a variety of genres, especially R&B, EDM and Soca music.
It would be after approximately six years that in 2011 the company forced its first door open.
